1. *Prijateljem* se ne rađamo, već to postajemo tokom života. (We are not born as *friends*, but we become that during our lifetime.)
2. Želim da postanem *prijatelj* s tobom. (I want to become *friends* with you.)
3. On je moj *prijatelj* iz detinjstva. (He is my childhood *friend*.)
4. *Prijatelju*, hajde da idemo na piće kasnije večeras. (Hey, *friend*, let's go for a drink later tonight.)
5. Zajedno smo *prijatelji* već godinama. (We have been *friends* for years now.)
6. Ne mogu da verujem da si to uradio, ti nisi moj *prijatelj*. (I can't believe you did that, you are not my *friend*.)
7. Sve što želim je da budem *prijateljica* s tobom. (All I want is to be *friends* with you.)
8. On je *prijatelj* koji uvek stoji uz mene kada mi je teško. (He is the *friend* who always stands by me when things get tough.)
9. *Prijatelji* se često svađaju, ali na kraju uvek nađu zajednički jezik. ( *Friends* often argue, but they always find a common ground in the end.)
10. Ne mogu da verujem da si *prijateljima* dao prednost nad porodicom. (I can't believe you put *friends* before family.)